divs: Sighting DetailsAt 7pm I went outside with my canon 7mp powershot sd550, to my backyard to take pictures of the clouds after a storm, during sunset. Later as I was checking my pictures I noticed two objects hovering at a distance I'm not sure of. When I downloaded the picture to my computer is when I realized I took a picture of a UFO. I went outside again to see the area of the picture I took but I saw nothing. I think I didn't see the objects when I was taking pictures because at the time I was not wearing my glasses.
